ted spray conditions and the predicted number of\ndroplets agrees well with those measured. For gas turbine engine combustion\nresearch, the developed framework is of importance, as it facilitates\nunderstanding the time-resolved spray characteristics for instances that the\nspray data is available sparsely.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 11 Dec 2022 17:00:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-13"}
