t with our models. We also\nargue that the turbulent magnetic field has a significant impact on the\nconfinement of non-thermal electrons in the ALT region.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 12 Dec 2022 09:59:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-08"}
